flowRoot.flowPara: Judith has started a company entering the "maker" space. She's looking for a way to easily get her customers engaged with the products on her website.
Through her other online shopping experience, she has learned of PowerReviews. Looking at the API explorer, she decides it's easy to make it fit her needs.
The company is a hit! Judith's customers are able to engage with both her products and each other, creating a thriving marketplace.
